---
import SimpleLayout from '../layouts/SimpleLayout.astro';
---

<SimpleLayout title="Start Here" description="The best of my writing and work — curated so you can jump straight in." url="/start-here">
  <section class="link-list">
    <p class="link-list__intro">
      Hi, I'm Sambath. Here's the best of what I've written and built — no categories, just the good stuff.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="/blog/2025-02-12-sentinel-objects/">Beyond None: Mastering Sentinel Objects for Cleaner Python Code</a>
        — Clean code practices that scale
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/blog/2025-02-20-local-git-server/">Why I had to build a Local Git Server</a>
        — Pragmatic problem-solving under constraints
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/cv">View my CV</a>
        — Experience and skills
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/sambaths" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        — Open source and side projects
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
        — Let's work together
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</SimpleLayout>

<style>
  .link-list {
    max-width: 36rem;
  }

  .link-list__intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .link-list ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .link-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .link-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .link-list a {
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
